MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-0879. State ex rel. Letcher v. Keco Industries, Inc.

Franklin App. No. 07AP-151, 2008-0hio-1907. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for *1420dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
